<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0045a" xml:id="I01.0017.0045a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0045a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 17</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0045a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>夫蒙文慶造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0045a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一</cb:mulu><head>之一</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0045a0101">　　　　　　　戊<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">戌</unclear>□□
<lb ed="I" n="0045a02" type="honorific"/>　神龜二年<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歲次</unclear>□月戊申朔十五日
<lb ed="I" n="0045a03" type="honorific"/>　　　　夫蒙文慶為<note n="0045001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30434"/>＝亡【史】</note><note n="0045001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30434"/>【佛拓】，亡【史】</note><app n="0045001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30434"/></rdg></app>父
<lb ed="I" n="0045a04" type="honorific"/>　　　　<app type="star" corresp="#0045001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30434"/></rdg></app>妹。七世父母。因緣
<lb ed="I" n="0045a05" type="honorific"/>　　　　　眷蜀。　造立石
<lb ed="I" n="0045a06" type="honorific"/>　　　　　像一區。減<note n="0045002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30428"/>＝割【史】</note><note n="0045002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30428"/>【佛拓】，割【史】</note><app n="0045002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">割</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30428"/></rdg></app>家<note n="0045003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30437"/>＝珍【史】</note><note n="0045003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30437"/>【佛拓】，珍【史】</note><app n="0045003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">珍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30437"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0045a07" type="honorific"/>　　　　雇良匠。仰感帝主覆
<lb ed="I" n="0045a08" type="honorific"/>　　　　　被之恩。追所生顯育
<lb ed="I" n="0045a09" type="honorific"/>　　　　　之重。<note n="0045004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">竒＝奇【史】</note><note n="0045004" resp="ihp" type="mod">竒【佛拓】，奇【史】</note><app n="0045004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">竒</rdg></app>形異容。則
<lb ed="I" n="0045a10" type="honorific"/>　　　　□明工不能加其巧。是
<lb ed="I" n="0045a11" type="honorific"/>　妻雷男帋<note n="0045005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥼶＝釋【史】</note><note n="0045005" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥼶【佛拓】，釋【史】</note><app n="0045005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">釋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥼶</rdg></app>迦<note n="0045006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">皼＝鼓【史】</note><note n="0045006" resp="ihp" type="mod">皼【佛拓】，鼓【史】</note><app n="0045006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">皼</rdg></app>法。豈非極</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二</cb:mulu><head>之二</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0045b0101">　　　　　　像主夫蒙文慶
<lb ed="I" n="0045b02" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　母雷□帋
<lb ed="I" n="0045b03" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　父名道明□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">靈</unclear>武
<lb ed="I" n="0045b04" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　妻瓽智□
<lb ed="I" n="0045b05" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">祖名</unclear>□□
<lb ed="I" n="0045b06" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　曾祖名屈閏
<lb ed="I" n="0045b07" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　□平縣令
<lb ed="I" n="0045b08" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　建□將軍<note n="0045007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">冝＝宜【史】</note><note n="0045007" resp="ihp" type="mod">冝【佛拓】，宜【史】</note><app n="0045007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">宜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">冝</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0045b09" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　高祖名南地姚□
<lb ed="I" n="0045b10" type="honorific"/>　　　　　高祖名脫帋娥</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045c00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之三</cb:mulu><head>之三</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0045c0101">　　　　　　聖姿　之形容。□
<lb ed="I" n="0045c02" type="honorific"/>　　　　　<note n="0045008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30438"/>＝徒【史】</note><note n="0045008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30438"/>【佛拓】，徒【史】</note><app n="0045008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">徒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30438"/></rdg></app><note n="0045009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥘇＝禮【史】</note><note n="0045009" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥘇【佛拓】，禮【史】</note><app n="0045009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥘇</rdg></app>敬。莫不<note n="0045010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啔＝啟【史】</note><note n="0045010" resp="ihp" type="mod">啔【佛拓】，啟【史】</note><app n="0045010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啔</rdg></app>悟。願
<lb ed="I" n="0045c03" type="honorific"/>　　　　　使龍華三會。恒在初首。
<lb ed="I" n="0045c04" type="honorific"/>清信士　　　佛弟子清信士<app type="star" corresp="#0045001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30434"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0045c05" type="honorific"/>　光姬　　　光姬。願使生天。妙
<lb ed="I" n="0045c06" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　朗國土<note n="0045c0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0045c0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">咎</unclear>。略受佛<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">記</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0045c07" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　若<note n="0045011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">堕＝墮【史】</note><note n="0045011" resp="ihp" type="mod">堕【佛拓】，墮【史】</note><app n="0045011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">墮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">堕</rdg></app>三<app type="star" corresp="#0045008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">徒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30438"/></rdg></app>。速得解<note n="0045012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨔫＝退【史】</note><note n="0045012" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨔫【佛拓】，退【史】</note><app n="0045012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">退</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨔫</rdg></app>。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045d00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之四</cb:mulu><head>之四</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0045d01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0045d0101">　　　　　妻清信士雷豐供<note n="0045013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30439"/>＝養【史】</note><note n="0045013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30439"/>【佛拓】，養【史】</note><app n="0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛時
<lb ed="I" n="0045d02" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　蒙文慶供<app type="star" corresp="#0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛時
<lb ed="I" n="0045d03" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　佛弟子息祖慶供<app type="star" corresp="#0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛
<lb ed="I" n="0045d04" type="honorific"/>　　　合門大小善願從心功廣成就
<lb ed="I" n="0045d05" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　佛弟子息道郎供<app type="star" corresp="#0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛時
<lb ed="I" n="0045d06" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　清信女<note n="0045014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤋜＝照【史】</note><note n="0045014" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤋜【佛拓】，照【史】</note><app n="0045014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤋜</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0045007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">宜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">冝</rdg></app>供<app type="star" corresp="#0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛
<lb ed="I" n="0045d07" type="honorific"/>　清信女和如供<app type="star" corresp="#0045013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">養</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30439"/></rdg></app>佛時</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
